Package org.soulwing.prospecto.api.options

Option configuration for views, view writers, and view readers

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Options
    A map-like API for accessing context options.
    ReaderKeys
    Keys used for configuration options of a ViewReader.
    ViewDefaults
    Default values for various view options.
    ViewKeys
    Keys for view configuration options.
    WriterKeys
    Keys used for configuration options of a ViewWriter.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    OptionsMap
    An Options collection implemented on top of a Map.
